library('NbClust')
NbClust(data = X, distance = "euclidean", min.nc=2, max.nc=8, 
            method = "complete", index = "all")

FkM estàndar

# stand = 1 : estandaritza dades (x-u)/s
fkm <- FKM(X = Mc[,1:(ncol(Mc) - 1)], 
           k = 6, 
           m = 1.5, 
           stand = 1, 
           RS = 10)
VCV2(fkm$Xca, fkm$U, 2)
